207
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:23,150
The ultimate goal we hope to achieve is, for example,

208
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,730
Raft has three nodes

209
00:08:24,730 --> 00:08:28,040
We want to model these three nodes as a state machine

210
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,320
a single-threaded state machine, right

211
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,980
This is what Raft ultimately aims to accomplish.

212
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,500
but if there are other cases, for example

213
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:36,620
A request has come in

214
